{
  "stem": "985.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every-- whoever comes in stays there, sleeps there, and whatever meager food she had, she-- she-- she was feeding us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we stayed there for three, four days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then-- then continued, then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I found out that one girl from our town had a sister who had-- who was married, at that time, to a very influential person in-- from Russia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They came from Russia, and he became the head of the petroleum industry of the-- they call it-- [INAUDIBLE] in Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this friend of mine went over there, and she gave us a job as chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She, since I learned how to work in an auto shop-- a repair shop-- I learned how to drive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she gave us a job so to-- to drive them, to be their personal chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was an-- an old stable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They give us a room there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so it was fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we stayed there for about-- oh, for about four or five weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I decided-- he fell in love with this girl, but that's a long story.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- she-- she-- she didn't want him, anyway, but he stayed there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I left for the West, which was at the American-occupied territory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I subsequently wound up in Salzburg, in Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was supposed to stay there for one day and then go, the following day, to-- to Munich, with a-- with a transport of Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nobody sent-- no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we left Poland--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not quite.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there was a camp, but-- but that wasn't like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we left Po-- when we-- as I say, I left Poland with some other people, but not this particular friend who's been with me all the time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we-- we-- we ran out of different papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
